replyContent: Sorry for the trouble! Unfortunately, we don't control downloads, that's all Google. General advice when Google downloads fail is to delete partial downloads and restart your device.   I will contact their support as well, as this should not be happening.  In the meantime, if you'd like a refund, just email support@thup.com and we can provide.
